This object represents a filled quadrangle (box) with a intersection. The quadrangle has the given four corner points ( x_1, y_1 ), ( x_2, y_2 ), ( x_4, y_4 ) and ( x_5, y_5 ) as its border points. Where ( x_i, y_i ) is the neighbour point of ( x_{i+1}, y_{i+1} ). The point p_3 (x_3, y_3) is the intersection point. The intersection is located on the line betwean ( x_1, y_1 ) ( x_4, y_4 ) and the line betwean ( x_2, y_2 ) ( x_5, y_5 ) . The lines betwean ( x_1, y_1 ), ( x_2, y_2 ) and ( x_4, y_4 ), ( x_5, y_5 ) are intersection free. This object is a help object of the main Fib object.
